{"tid":667030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地產經紀馬路中心派樓盤傳單搶客　遭穿梭巴狂撞口鼻噴血","createTime":"2018-05-16T11:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T12:41:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c45ea02ceb52a6f1828b789b5842ece55d9e8777","tid":667030,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/large/1526469414_b1b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526469414_b1b0.jpg&h=014ce323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被小巴撞倒的地產經紀，口鼻流血當場昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳清水灣道發生交通意外，傍晚近6時，現場為新樓盤傲瀧對開，一名地產經紀於路中向途經駕駛人士派發樓盤傳單，其間遭一部向坑口方向行駛的穿梭巴撞倒，他飛彈數米，口鼻流血重創當場昏迷。傷者事後由救護車送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救。警方正調查原因。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/large/1526467651_af4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526467651_af4f.jpg&h=dde0a19c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傷者事後由救護車送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救。(溫文學攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/large/1526469416_b529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526469416_b529.jpg&h=05e6ac4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地產經紀被撞後倒在路中心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/large/1526469795_3646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526469795_3646.jpg&h=6235660f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車收掣不及，於是撞上前方的小巴。（姜偉康攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/large/1526469796_64b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526469796_64b0.jpg&h=6d7a47c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小巴的擋風玻璃爆裂，地上遺下一份傳單。（姜偉康攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/large/1526469797_6f81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526469797_6f81.jpg&h=26db0343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將軍澳傲瀧對開發生交通意外。（姜偉康攝）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180516/58200700?_ga=2.239352003.151545489.1526470318-108976815.1526470318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58200700%3F_ga%3D2.239352003.151545489.1526470318-108976815.1526470318&d=qOvJIoHipGfKSpPHgSLS3tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9c7e299e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58200700%3F_ga%3D2.239352003.151545489.1526470318-108976815.1526470318&h=5308b729\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180516/58200700?_ga=2.239352003.151545489.1526470318-108976815.1526470318</a>"},{"pid":"ccd3904ee03ba33f9022acb19e6422f664ddf119","tid":667030,"uid":155080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"死人地產佬害咗個小巴司機"},{"pid":"55ae6f3e3f63db8aabbd2f71281e2bb3feff2c81","tid":667030,"uid":6424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"狂依個字，唔係痴線佬就係講人不能自控/不停做<br />\n到底標題應該用邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031b8bc894618b4f1b0852d8cba5d412c0176c42","tid":667030,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/195710_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F195710_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=15e8aeb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b189d82f55291e6720203a632c